1955;;The Blue Peter;;British;;Wolf Rilla;;Kieron Moore, Sarah Lawson;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Blue_Peter_(1955_film);;Shellshocked following his experiences as a POW, naval war hero Mike Merriworth (Kieron Moore) enrols as a physical instructor at an Outward Bound sea school in Wales, and discovers new purpose shaping the lives of the boys in his charge.